クラス TimewindowInformationFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • manhattan.timewindow.TimewindowInformationFile

  • public final class TimewindowInformationFile
extends java.lang.Object
    time window の情報をいれてあるファイル 1 time window 32 byte String station (8), String of GlobalCMTID (15), component (1),
    Float starting time (4) (Round off to the third decimal place.),
    Float end time (4) (Round off to the third decimal place.),
